* Carnage smiled at Tankorr but then starts jumping out of the way each time 
that he slashes at her. She had to admit that he was a bit slow but he was 
fast enough to keep her on her feet, as she dodges out of the way of yet 
another swipe she aims her pistil the best she can and hires at his chest.
She then danced out of the way of another slash but then grabs both of 
Tankorr's arms, careful to avoid the blades and smiles at him...*

" Care to dance?"

* She puts her weight into a push that should at least bring him off of 
balance, she laughs...this WAS fun!*
